Porn Policy - Newbie/Question Forum Policy
</font>
</td>
<TD valign=top>
<FONT SIZE="1" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
<IMG SRC="http://www.aq2zone.com/ubb/posticonnew.gif"  BORDER=0 ALT="New Announcement!"> posted by XCheckR&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<FONT SIZE="1" FACE="Verdana, Arial" COLOR="#ff0000">(01-01-2000 through 01-01-2525)</FONT><HR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">PORN POLICY<P>Porn Policy:<BR> <BR>Effective immediately the following policy shall be enforced:<BR> <BR>There is to be no posting of pornographic pictures or links to pornographic pictures or sites on this message board.  <BR>For our purposes, we will use the PG-13 rule of what we consider porn.  Please remember that we cannont prevent minors<BR>from viewing this board so we must insist on this rule.<BR> <BR>If you post something that is in violation of this policy, we will remove it immediately and issue one warning.  After that, we will remove your accout from this board.  Please note that if you post something extremely offensive, we will ban you without a warning.<BR> <BR>Thank you for your cooperation.<P> <P>Re: The New Forum<BR>1) No flaming will be tolerated in the new forum, this could result in a ban. You will recieve one warning, second offense will get you banned.<BR>2) Please try to be courteous to new  players, they may not understand our joking about and may take it the wrong way.<BR>3) Remember you were a newbie once too, the forum is also for vets to ask questions.<BR>4) As mentioned in the porn policy, there are lots of minors on this board so be careful of what you say.<BR>5) To insure fairness, all ban situations are evaluated by a group of admins, not just one person. <P></FONT>
